
Codes for generating private and public keys for Kinesis Firehose integration with Snowflake:

 Linux / MacOS 
 ------------------------


openssl genrsa 2048 | openssl pkcs8 -topk8 -inform PEM -out private_key.p8 -nocrypt


 Windows PowerShell 
 ------------------------
(Get-Content private_key.p8) -notmatch "-----" -join "" | Set-Content -NoNewline private_key_kinesis.txt



openssl rsa -in private_key.p8 -pubout -out public_key.pub

